short_description:
The company that use the bacula for backup cloud, will can offer for your clients, through your email, access a Web System, where it will can see  informations about the backup and backup server, for example:
- Backup history;
- How much it will pay in the month's end per backup storage and generate billet to pay it;
- Payment history;
- Logic Informations about the backup server (Graphics with the status of HD, Memory, I/O, network..);
- Other informations, like, business rule of service, rule access of users.
